33. The Disciplinary Committee may order any one or any
combination of two or more of the following:
(a)  the issuance of a written reprimand;
(b) the imposition  of  a  fine  not  exceeding  five
thousand ringgit;
(c) suspension for a period not exceeding one year;
(d) cancellation of registration.
